WEBVTT

00:00:14.549 --> 00:00:17.445
You know, I had a real rough time
in school with ADD,

00:00:17.469 --> 00:00:18.625
and I have a PhD.

00:00:18.649 --> 00:00:20.989
I earned a PhD, but ...
tough to pay attention --

00:00:21.013 --> 00:00:24.805
biology, geology, physics,
chemistry -- really tough for me.

00:00:24.829 --> 00:00:26.796
Only one thing grabbed my attention,

00:00:26.820 --> 00:00:30.231
and it's that planet called Earth.